OL,3,CTributes paid as former Manchester ice
OL,4,Chockey star dies
OL,6,FTributes are being paid to the former
OL,7,FManchester Storm ice hockey star Wade
OL,8,FMacLeod, who has died aged 38.
OL,10,FCanadian forward MacLeod signed for
OL,11,FStorm in August 2021 and left the
OL,12,FElite Hockey League outfit by mutual
OL,13,Fconsent in November of the same year.
OL,15,FBefore joining Storm, he underwent
OL,16,Ffour separate operations for brain
OL,17,Ftumours, plus chemotherapy and
OL,18,Fradiotherapy. One of the surgeries
OL,19,Fmeant he lost his speech for almost
OL,20,Ftwo months.
