OL,6,FStorm posted on their Instagram page:
OL,7,F"We are heartbroken to learn of the
OL,8,Fpassing of former Storm player, Wade
OL,9,FMacLeod.
OL,11,F"He was a true warrior, and his spirit
OL,12,Fwill forever be part of the Storm
OL,13,Ffamily.
OL,15,F"Our deepest condolences go out to his
OL,16,Fwife Karly, their two daughters, and
OL,17,Fall of Wade's loved ones at this
OL,18,Fincredibly difficult time."
