OL,6,FIn August 2021, just after signing for
OL,7,FStorm, MacLeod told our sports
OL,8,Fcorrespondent Chris Hall that he was
OL,9,Flooking forward to getting back on the
OL,10,Fice after his three-year absence due
OL,11,Fto illness: "When I take my first hit,
OL,12,Fit's going to get me going," he says,
OL,13,Fexcitedly.
OL,15,F"Whatever hits come my way, I'll take
OL,16,Fin my stride."
